summary: Liquid has secured a $7.6 million seed round led by Paradigm. The platform facilitates trading from any location with leverage options up to 150x, promising a user-friendly interface with instant risk visibility. Liquid has facilitated over $2 billion in trades and boasts 20,000+ signups, with 24/7 market availability and significantly lower trading fees—cutting costs by 90% compared to platforms like Coinbase. The platform is decentralized, non-custodial, and offers users strategy-based trading with a historical average yield of ~10% APY. Users can access the platform via iOS and Android apps.
